Title: Fix KeyError on mknotifyd start after upgrade to 2.1.0
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: notifications
Date: 1653399002
Edition: cee
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.2.0i1

If the notification spooler was used on a remote site, after upgrade to 2.1.0
the start of the mknotifyd could fail with the error "KeyError: 'encryption'".
